<BaseLayout title="Public Data Downloads | CourtScope"><section class="section"><div class="shell"><h1>Public data</h1><p>Downloadable releases will include provenance, schema, methodology association, checksum, reuse terms, and clear raw/normalized/derived/sample labels.</p><div class="notice warning"><strong>Fixture-only downloads.</strong> These files contain synthetic records for development and must not be represented as court data.</div><div class="grid grid-3"><article class="card"><p class="eyebrow">CSV</p><h2>Fixture cases</h2><p>Broadly compatible tabular format.</p><a class="button" href="/downloads/cases-fixture.csv">Download CSV</a></article><article class="card"><p class="eyebrow">JSON</p><h2>Fixture cases</h2><p>Machine-readable structured records.</p><a class="button" href="/downloads/cases-fixture.json">Download JSON</a></article><article class="card"><p class="eyebrow">Parquet</p><h2>Fixture cases</h2><p>Efficient research format.</p><a class="button" href="/downloads/cases-fixture.parquet">Download Parquet</a></article></div><h2>Release contract</h2><ul><li>Dataset-specific terms</li><li>English field names and values</li><li>Small-cell suppression when needed</li><li>Historic releases retained</li><li>Checksums published alongside artifacts</li></ul></div></section></BaseLayout>
